  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p>\r\n<p>Heat a&nbsp;large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong> bacon</strong> and cook for 2 min on each side or until crispy</p>\r\n<p>Remove the <strong>bacon</strong> from the pan, roughly chop into small pieces and set aside &ndash; this is your<strong> bacon topping</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Peel and chop&nbsp;the<strong> red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Trim, then dice the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>&nbsp;over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and cook for 5 min or until softened</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped courgette</strong>&nbsp;with half the&nbsp;<strong>chopped garlic</strong> (save the rest for later!) and cook for 2 min further</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the <strong>chicken&nbsp;stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in 700ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.3L]</span>&nbsp;<strong>boiled water</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>chicken&nbsp;stock</strong>, <strong>cannellini beans</strong> and <strong>kale</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook for 10 min &ndash; this is your <strong>vegetable &amp; bean soup</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>basil leaves</strong>&nbsp;to a <strong>pestle &amp; mortar</strong> with the&nbsp;<strong>remaining&nbsp;garlic</strong>&nbsp;(Don't like raw garlic? Go easy!) and grind to a smooth<strong>&nbsp;paste</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>olive oil </strong>and give it a good mix up</p>\r\n<p>Tip: if you don't have a pestle &amp; mortar, chop the basil leaves very finely and mix with olive oil</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>grated cheese</strong> to the<strong>&nbsp;basil paste </strong>and give everything a good mix up<strong>&nbsp;</strong>&ndash;&nbsp;this is your <strong>pistou</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1607.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
